properties.sfomuseum:description: 8 1/2 x 11 newsletter, folded. Pre-Aug 1940 on newsprint. Usually 8 pages; later issues 16-20 pages. Pages 3-6 are on removable inner sheet. Aug 30, 1947 and later printed on less acidic paper; housed in separate folders.
